N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 2397.9 - Rule of construction

State Regulations

The provisions of Subchapters A and B of Chapter III, and

Subchapter A of Chapter IV, of this Title, shall apply to taxpayers
participating in the program unless the provisions of this Part are
inconsistent therewith, in which case the provisions of this Part shall
govern. Notes
